{"word":"ἀνάντης","slug":"ἀνάντης","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνάντης</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ἀνά, ἀντάω</el>\n<p/><i>up-hill, steep</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>; <el>πρὸς τὸ ἄναντες</el> to <i>the highest point</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/>"}]}